# QuantFlow — Coding Standards & Conventions

> **Project:** QuantFlow — Low-code Crypto Trading Platform (Binance Futures CEX)
> **Tech Stack:** Go 1.24 (Clean Architecture) · Next.js 16 / React 19 / TypeScript · PostgreSQL 16 · Docker Compose · Nginx
> **Version:** 1.0

